{"type":"message","id":"ac6c2b23","parentId":"01a56777","timestamp":"2026-04-03T21:09:36.073Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_Gs9LXUqHALbweM8Hjw2SzcYO|fc_0bec8cc91ee6e9930169d02c8f7fa881919974ae49bccfa4ec","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"C:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\docs\\openclaw_integration.md:178: | `b2_bootstrap_ready.json` | b2_director | Director has loaded the bootstrap contract and is ready |\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\docs\\openclaw_integration.md:188: b2_bootstrap_ready.json\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\docs\\openclaw_integration.md:488: 5. Poll for b2_bootstrap_ready.json             (director is ready)\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\docs\\project_structure.md:4: **Status:** Architecture Definition (pre-implementation)\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\docs\\project_structure.md:686: Response: { \"status\": \"complete\", \"checkpoint\": \"screenplay_done.json\" }\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\docs\\runbook.md:70: - Check KMS dashboard for key status\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\docs\\runbook.md:79: - **Lock mechanism:** Status column E changed to \"processing\" atomically\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\docs\\runbook.md:96: ### \"No scripts with status 'to do' found\"\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\docs\\runbook.md:97: All scripts in the Google Sheet have been used. Add new scripts or reset status.\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\docs\\v2_context.md:5: **Status:** Planning Phase\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\docs\\cfv3_blocs\\bloco1_agents_and_prompts.md:321: 3. If no ke