factory\\docs\\paperclip_master\\00_OVERVIEW.md:167: - Issue status changes\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\docs\\paperclip_master\\00_OVERVIEW.md:184: | `companies` | Multi-tenant root | `id`, `name`, `status` |\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\docs\\paperclip_master\\00_OVERVIEW.md:186: | `heartbeat_runs` | Execution history | `id`, `agent_id`, `status`, `source`, `started_at` |\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\docs\\paperclip_master\\00_OVERVIEW.md:187: | `issues` | Task tracking | `id`, `company_id`, `status`, `assigned_to`, `checkout_run_id` |\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\docs\\paperclip_master\\00_OVERVIEW.md:188: | `projects` | Project containers | `id`, `company_id`, `status` |\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\docs\\paperclip_master\\00_OVERVIEW.md:190: | `approvals` | Governance decisions | `id`, `company_id`, `type`, `status` |\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\docs\\paperclip_master\\00_OVERVIEW.md:307: ## 8. Roadmap Status (as of April 2026)\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\docs\\paperclip_master\\01_INSTALLATION_SETUP.md:442: # Expected: {\"status\":\"ok\"}\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\docs\\paperclip_master\\01_INSTALLATION_SETUP.md:457: - **Agent status**: See which agents are idle, running, paused, or in error\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\docs\\paperclip_master\\01_INSTALLATION_SETUP.md:458: - **Task board**: View open issues, assignments, and completion status\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\docs\\paperclip_master\\01_INSTALLATION_SETUP.md:523: 1. Check agent status: `paperclipai agent list --company-id <id>`\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-fact