ntent_factory\\docs\\paperclip_master\\08_TASKS_ISSUES.md:415: | `action` | What was done (created, updated, status_changed, checked_out, etc.) |\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\docs\\paperclip_master\\08_TASKS_ISSUES.md:422: - Issue creation, status changes, assignment changes\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\docs\\paperclip_master\\08_TASKS_ISSUES.md:457: - Status changes\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\docs\\paperclip_master\\08_TASKS_ISSUES.md:474: 8. **Update progress**: `PATCH /api/issues/{issueId}` with status and comments\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\docs\\paperclip_master\\09_ROUTINES.md:68: | `status` | enum | `queued`, `running`, `succeeded`, `failed` |\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\docs\\paperclip_master\\09_ROUTINES.md:287: **Run statuses**:\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\docs\\paperclip_master\\09_ROUTINES.md:289: | Status | Description |\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\docs\\paperclip_master\\09_ROUTINES.md:302: - Final status\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\docs\\paperclip_master\\09_ROUTINES.md:317: - **Run history**: Chronological list of all runs with status\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\docs\\paperclip_master\\10_API_REFERENCE.md:102: ## 4. HTTP Status Codes\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\docs\\paperclip_master\\10_API_REFERENCE.md:113: | 422 | Invalid state transition | Review workflow rules; check current status |\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\docs\\paperclip_master\\10_API_REFERENCE.md:151: | PATCH | `/api/issues/{issueId}` | Update issue (status, assignment, add comment) |\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\docs\\paperclip_master\\10_API_REFERENCE.md:162: | `status` | string | Filter by status (todo, in_progress, blocked, etc.) |\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\docs\\paperclip_master\\10_API_REFERENCE.md:174: \"expectedStatuses\": [\"todo\", \"backlog\", \"blocked\"]\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\docs\\paperclip_master\\10_API_REFERENCE.md:184: \"status\": \"in_progress\",\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\docs\\paperclip_master\\10_API_REFERENCE.md:230: | `status` | string | Filter by status (queued, running, succeeded, failed, timed_out, cancelled) |\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\docs\\paperclip_master\\10_API_REFERENCE.md:314: | Heartbeat run status changes | `queued` -> `running` -> `succeeded`/`failed` |\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\docs\\paperclip_master\\10_API_REFERENCE.md:315: | Agent status transitions | `idle` -> `running` -> `idle` |\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\docs\\paperclip_master\\10_API_REFERENCE.md:316: | Issue status changes | Status transitions on any issue |\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\docs\\paperclip_master\\10_API_REFERENCE.md:363: | `paperclipai issue list` | List issues (filterable by company, status, agent) |\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\docs\\paperclip_master\\10_API_REFERENCE.md:374: | `--status <string>` | Initial status (default: `todo`) |\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\docs\\paperclip_master\\10_API_REFERENCE.md:523: claimQueuedRun(runId);  // status: queued -> running\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\docs\\paperclip_master\\10_API_REFERENCE.md:538: publishLiveEvent({ type: \"run_completed\", runId, status: \"succeeded\" });\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\docs\\paperclip_master\\10_API_REFERENCE.md:703: 2. GET  /api/companies/{cid}/issues?assigneeAgentId={aid}&status=in_progress  # Resume work?\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\docs\\paperclip_master\\10_API_REFERENCE.md:704: 3. GET  /api/companies/{cid}/issues?assigneeAgentId={aid}&status=todo         # New work?\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\docs\\paperclip_master\\11_SECRETS_ENV.md:200: - **Status updates**: `POST /api/issues/{issueId}/comments`\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\docs\\paperclip_master\\11_SECRETS_ENV.md:216: # Heartbeat -- check for pending work, report status\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\docs\\paperclip_master\\12_BUDGET_GOVERNANCE.md:115: - Agent status changes to `paused`\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\docs\\paperclip_master\\12_BUDGET_GOVERNANCE.md:258: - `status` -- current state\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\docs\\paperclip_master\\12_BUDGET_GOVERNANCE.md:268: 2. Paperclip intercepts and creates an approval record with status `pending`\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\docs\\paperclip_master\\12_BUDGET_GOVERNANCE.md:338: | Project Manager | Claude Haiku 3.5 | Routing tasks, status checks, simple delegation -- speed matters more than depth | $0.80 input / $4 output |\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\docs\\paperclip_master\\12_BUDGET_GOVERNANCE.md:549: - ~500 tokens per heartbeat (status check) = 4.3M tokens/month just for heartbeats\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\docs\\paperclip_master\\13_GOTCHAS_LIMITATIONS.md:52: 7. Update task status\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\docs\\paperclip_master\\13_GOTCHAS_LIMITATIONS.md:157: | Missing Approval Type | Impact | Status |\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\docs\\paperclip_master\\13_GOTCHAS_LIMITATIONS.md:506: ~500 tokens/heartbeat (identity + task check + status report)\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\docs\\workflows\\w1_screenplay.md:3: **Status:** Production (tested 2026-04-02)\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\docs\\workflows\\w1_screenplay.md:35: 2. Fetch script from Google Sheets (atomic lock  status \"processing\")\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\docs\\workflows\\w1_screenplay.md:50: | Google Sheets | Script text (status \"to do\") | Yes (unless --script provided) |\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\docs\\workflows\\w2_tts_audio.md:3: **Status:** Production (tested 2026-04-03)\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\docs\\workflows\\w3_block2.md:3: **Status**: Production (S3-only mode validated 2026-04-03)\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\docs\\workflows\\w3_block2.md:57: ��� state/b2_state.json\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\docs\\workflows\\w3_block2.md:59: �   ��� b2_bootstrap_ready.json\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\docs\\workflows\\w3_block2.md:87: - Status: completed","cwd":"C:\\Users\\User-OEM\\.openclaw\\agents\\b2_director"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775250576065}}
