ocs\\openclaw_integration.md:178: | `b2_bootstrap_ready.json` | b2_director | Director has loaded the bootstrap contract and is ready |\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\docs\\openclaw_integration.md:179: | `s3_requested.json` | b2_director | Director is requesting S3 visual planning to begin |\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\docs\\openclaw_integration.md:188: b2_bootstrap_ready.json\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\docs\\openclaw_integration.md:189: s3_requested.json\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\docs\\openclaw_integration.md:295: Written by the director (inside `s3_requested.json`) and consumed by the SM.\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\docs\\openclaw_integration.md:488: 5. Poll for b2_bootstrap_ready.json             (director is ready)\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\docs\\openclaw_integration.md:489: 6. Poll for s3_requested.json                   (director wants S3)\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\docs\\openclaw_integration.md:490: 7. Extract SM bootstrap from s3_requested.json\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\pipeline\\workflows\\w3_block2.py:255: \"bootstrap_checkpoint_path\": str(sector_root / \"checkpoints\" / \"s3_bootstrap_ready.json\"),\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\pipeline\\workflows\\w3_block2.py:364: f\"Escreva em {b2_root}: state/b2_state.json, checkpoints/b2_bootstrap_ready.json, checkpoints/s3_requested.json. \"\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\pipeline\\workflows\\w3_block2.py:374: target_checkpoints=[\"s3_requested.json\", \"b2_completed.json\", \"b2_failed.json\"],\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\content-factory\\auto_content_factory\\pipeline\\workfl