{"type":"message","id":"97b33783","parentId":"4e87c934","timestamp":"2026-04-03T21:10:06.213Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_MIZ6JSqoP86noSIYOjMG2rvw|fc_0bec8cc91ee6e9930169d02cadd398819180f9b474553588fa","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\nFor a single video with S3 only:\n\n```\n1. Clean sessions for all B2/S3 agents\n2. Create b2/ directory structure (checkpoints/, sectors/s3_visual_planning/...)\n3. Write b2_bootstrap.json with mode: \"s3_only\"\n4. Launch b2_director with bootstrap message\n5. Poll for b2_bootstrap_ready.json             (director is ready)\n6. Poll for s3_requested.json                   (director wants S3)\n7. Extract SM bootstrap from s3_requested.json\n8. Launch sm_s3_visual_planning with bootstrap\n9. Poll for s3_completed.json                   (SM finished S3)\n10. Build resume message (reason: s3_completed)\n11. Launch b2_director with resume message\n12. Poll for b2_completed.json                  (director closed block)\n13. Read b2_completed.json for final artefact paths\n14. Report results to Perseus (Paperclip side)\n```\n\nFor a full block with S3+S4+S5+S6, repeat steps 6-12 for each sector.\n\n---\n\n## Appendix: Debugging Checklist\n\nWhen a run fails:\n\n1. **Check the checkpoint directory** -- did any checkpoint file get written?\n2. **Read the OpenClaw log file** -- look for the agent's stdout/stderr in `data/openclaw_logs/`\n\n[12 more lines in file. Use offset=510 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775250606201}}
